To use the libraries in arduino:
1. Copy utility into both GameOfLightSim and GameOfLightHW
2. Copy GameOfLightSim and GameOfLightHW into <your-arduino-folder>/libraries/
3. Import the library you need into your program in Arudino IDE
4. Make a GameOfLightSim/GameOfLightHW object (e.g. GameOfLightSim frame; )
5. Use it.
6. ??
7. Profit
